History expansion
!!      ->  Last command-line
!*      ->  Arguments of last command
!^      ->  First argument of last command
!$      ->  Last argument of last command

Glob qualifiers
*(.)    ->  Plain files
*(/)    ->  Directories
*(m0)   ->  Last modified today
*(m-4)  ->  Last modified <4 days ago 

Common Commands
..      ->  cd ..
...     ->  cd ../..
s       ->  sudo
c       ->  clear
h       ->  history

Directory Operations
md      ->  mkdir -p
rd      ->  rmdir


